        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 drop-shadow-lg font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 via-yellow-500 to-green-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                    Pourquoi devenir membre ?
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Découvrez les raisons qui font de Binajia une communauté unique
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                {% set raisons = [
                    {
                        icon: 'M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z',
